1000000 == F_CPU

REQUIRE {SET}     lib/ports.spf

PD7 WIRE LED

PB0 WIRE BTN_SELECT
PB1 WIRE BTN_UP
PB2 WIRE BTN_DOWN
PB3 WIRE BTN_EXIT

GROUP{ BTN_SELECT BTN_UP BTN_DOWN BTN_EXIT }GROUP BUTTONS

